<dt class="title">
<dl class="lemmaWgt-lemmaTitle lemmaWgt-lemmaTitle-">
<dd class="lemmaWgt-lemmaTitle-title">
<h1 >一又二分之一的夏天</h1>
<a href="javascript:;" class="edit-lemma cmn-btn-hover-blue cmn-btn-28 j-edit-link"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_edit-lemma"></em>编辑</a>
<a class="lock-lemma" target="_blank" href="/view/10812319.htm" title="锁定"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_lock-lemma"></em>锁定</a>
</dd>
<dd class="lemmaWgt-lemmaTitle-keyInfo">
<ul>
<li>
中国内地
</li>
<li>
27集
</li>
</ul>
</dd>
</dl></dt>
<dd class="desc">
<div class="lemma-summary" label-module="lemmaSummary">
<div class="para" label-module="para">《一又二分之一的夏天》是由中国、韩国合作拍摄的校园浪漫清甜派偶像剧，由张林子执导，<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%B0%BC%E6%9F%A5%E5%9D%A4%C2%B7%E6%8A%94%E5%8B%92%E5%A8%81%E6%9F%A5%E5%9B%BA">尼查坤·抔勒威查固</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%BE%90%E7%92%90">徐璐</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E8%92%8B%E5%8A%B2%E5%A4%AB">蒋劲夫</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E4%BA%8E%E6%96%87%E6%96%87">于文文</a>、蒋劲夫、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E9%AB%98%E7%8F%91%E7%8F%82">高珑珂</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E4%BD%95%E5%A6%8D%E5%B8%8C">何妍希</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%91%A8%E6%B1%A4%E8%B1%AA">周汤豪</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%9C%B1%E4%B8%B9">朱丹</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%91%A8%E6%99%93%E9%B8%A5">周晓鸥</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%AD%9F%E4%BD%B3">孟佳</a>、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%9D%8E%E6%98%B6">李昶</a>等联袂出演。</div><div class="para" label-module="para">本剧讲述了几位90后的年轻人自由奔放的ABC张灏、肩负众望的李修齐、超级女汉子罗曼、搞笑达人马俊才等一群搞笑奇葩舍友们的校园生活。</div><div class="para" label-module="para">该剧已于2014年6月23日起东方卫视梦想剧场全国首播，后改为下午剧场播出。<sup>[1]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[1]_14771740">&nbsp;</a>
</div>
</div>
</dd>
<dd class="middleContent">
<div class="configModuleBanner">
</div></dd>
