<a name="角色介绍" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
</div><div class="para-title level-2" label-module="para-title">
<h2 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">一又二分之一的夏天</span>角色介绍</h2>
<a class="edit-icon j-edit-link" data-edit-dl="4" href="javascript:;"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_edit-lemma"></em>编辑</a>
</div>
<div class="anchor-list">
<a name="juesejieshao" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
</div><div class="lemmaWgt-roleIntroduction">
<ul>
<li class="roleIntroduction-item ">
<a class="roleIntrodcution-picture" href="/pic/%E4%B8%80%E5%8F%88%E4%BA%8C%E5%88%86%E4%B9%8B%E4%B8%80%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%8F%E5%A4%A9/6110331/0/d043ad4bd11373f0dbbec885a70f4bfbfbed0422?fr=lemma" target = "_blank">
<img src="https://gss1.bdstatic.com/9vo3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/crop%3D145%2C61%2C311%2C442%3Bw%3D138%3Bq%3D95/sign=f2d891657bf0f736ccb116413764872c/d043ad4bd11373f0dbbec885a70f4bfbfbed0422.jpg" alt=""/>
</a>
<dl class="roleIntrodcution-descritpion">
<dt>
<div class="role-name">
<span class="item-value">
<b>张灏</b>
</span>
</div>
<div class="role-actor">
<span class="item-key">演员</span><span class="item-value">
<b><a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%B0%BC%E5%9D%A4">尼坤</a></b>
</span>
</div>
<div class="role-voice">
</div>
</dt>
<dd class="role-description">
<div>美籍华侨国际学院大三学生</div><div>开朗、调皮、独立、执着、适应能力强、爱吃虾。为了曾经在圣托里尼岛邂逅并产生爱慕的中国女孩舒晴，决定独自来到厦门留学。到学校后参加了音乐社团，成了乐队的键盘手和主唱。在这里，他结识了乐队的指导教授、乐队成员。边打工边赚取生活费，边参加社团活动的同时，用尽所有剩余时间、精力以及关系网去寻找舒晴。后来发现对暗恋自己并一直在身边帮助自己的女孩罗曼产生了不寻常的感情。</div>
</dd>
</dl>
</li>
<li class="roleIntroduction-item ">
<a class="roleIntrodcution-picture" href="/pic/%E4%B8%80%E5%8F%88%E4%BA%8C%E5%88%86%E4%B9%8B%E4%B8%80%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%8F%E5%A4%A9/6110331/0/3b87e950352ac65cdbebc169f8f2b21193138a3a?fr=lemma" target = "_blank">
<img src="https://gss3.bdstatic.com/-Po3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/crop%3D110%2C154%2C350%2C492%3Bh%3D195%3Bq%3D95/sign=a6f1dd6023a446236a85ff22a513433e/3b87e950352ac65cdbebc169f8f2b21193138a3a.jpg" alt=""/>
</a>
<dl class="roleIntrodcution-descritpion">
<dt>
<div class="role-name">
<span class="item-value">
<b>罗曼</b>
</span>
</div>
<div class="role-actor">
<span class="item-key">演员</span><span class="item-value">
<b><a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%BE%90%E7%92%90">徐璐</a></b>
</span>
</div>
<div class="role-voice">
</div>
</dt>
<dd class="role-description">
<div>哲学系大三学生</div><div>乐观、开朗、上进、大大咧咧、爱吃面包。资质平平，成绩一般，缺少女人味、动作粗鲁、不爱打扮，不折不扣的假小子。在大学里，为了帮父亲保住大学讲师的位子，强迫，威逼利诱的情况下找来了男同学组建了乐队社团。与帅气的留学生张灏因为误会、打工、乐队而相熟。虽然刚开始两人像冤家对头，但随着深入的了解认识，感情一片空白的她，从张灏身上感受到了“爱情”。而从小照顾帮助她的青梅竹马李修齐也向她表白了爱慕。暗恋与被恋，使她的初恋处于不可预测的混乱状态。</div>
</dd>
</dl>
</li>
<li class="roleIntroduction-item ">
<a class="roleIntrodcution-picture" href="/pic/%E4%B8%80%E5%8F%88%E4%BA%8C%E5%88%86%E4%B9%8B%E4%B8%80%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%8F%E5%A4%A9/6110331/0/023b5bb5c9ea15cef5844713b5003af33a87b246?fr=lemma" target = "_blank">
<img src="https://gss3.bdstatic.com/-Po3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/crop%3D250%2C0%2C366%2C520%3Bw%3D138%3Bq%3D95/sign=6758d9d1f8edab64603d1780ca049af3/023b5bb5c9ea15cef5844713b5003af33a87b246.jpg" alt=""/>
</a>
<dl class="roleIntrodcution-descritpion">
<dt>
<div class="role-name">
<span class="item-value">
<b>李修齐</b>
</span>
</div>
<div class="role-actor">
<span class="item-key">演员</span><span class="item-value">
<a target=_blank href="/item/%E8%92%8B%E5%8A%B2%E5%A4%AB">蒋劲夫</a>
</span>
</div>
<div class="role-voice">
</div>
</dt>
<dd class="role-description">
<div>法学系大三学生</div><div>典型的完美主义者。很照顾人，得到了“知心哥哥”的称呼，做事循规蹈矩，有很强的原则性，与任何人相处都很和睦。在同龄男孩中显得格外稳重。为了父母的期望而努力，但是有时因此感到压抑。在罗曼的威胁下加入乐队，在乐队里，他学到了用音乐缓解压力的方法，他对青梅竹马罗曼一直都很照顾，总是帮她收拾残局。对罗曼的关心和担心，被罗曼视为啰嗦。他将对罗曼的爱意深藏在内心，但随着罗曼对张灏感情上的变化，而非常苦恼。他再也掩饰不住，最终向罗曼告白。</div>
</dd>
</dl>
</li>
<li class="roleIntroduction-item ">
<a class="roleIntrodcution-picture" href="/pic/%E4%B8%80%E5%8F%88%E4%BA%8C%E5%88%86%E4%B9%8B%E4%B8%80%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%8F%E5%A4%A9/6110331/0/0dd7912397dda1447a4acba8b1b7d0a20cf4866d?fr=lemma" target = "_blank">
<img src="https://gss3.bdstatic.com/7Po3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/crop%3D101%2C27%2C222%2C316%3Bw%3D138%3Bq%3D95/sign=f9a331e67fd98d10629b56711c0e883f/0dd7912397dda1447a4acba8b1b7d0a20cf4866d.jpg" alt=""/>
</a>
<dl class="roleIntrodcution-descritpion">
<dt>
<div class="role-name">
<span class="item-value">
<b>舒晴</b>
</span>
</div>
<div class="role-actor">
<span class="item-key">演员</span><span class="item-value">
<b><a target=_blank href="/item/%E4%BA%8E%E6%96%87%E6%96%87">于文文</a></b>
</span>
</div>
<div class="role-voice">
</div>
</dt>
<dd class="role-description">
<div>艺术大学大提琴专业的大三学生</div><div>冷艳、孤傲、沉默寡言。在严肃的父亲主导下顺从着父母的期待而活着，但是到了“结婚”终于爆发了，第一次试图反抗。她在父亲的安排下学习古典音乐，但内心深处喜爱并向往摇滚音乐。背着家人在酒吧做驻场表演。从未经历过恋爱的她，被父亲安排了企业联姻。她在圣托里尼岛见到了张灏，彼此相互吸引，但在父亲的威胁下没来得及跟张灏告别就回到了中国。在已认命的状态下张灏突然出现了，既害怕给张灏不好的影响，又没有勇气脱离父母的掌控，她只好假装不认识张灏，伤了张灏的心。</div>
</dd>
</dl>
</li>
</ul>
<div class="expand-all-container">
</div>
</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><i>角色介绍参考资料来源</i><sup>[5]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[5]_14771740">&nbsp;</a>
</div><div class="anchor-list">
<a name="5" class="lemma-anchor para-title" ></a>
<a name="sub14771740_5" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
<a name="音乐原声" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
</div><div class="para-title level-2" label-module="para-title">
<h2 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">一又二分之一的夏天</span>音乐原声</h2>
<a class="edit-icon j-edit-link" data-edit-dl="5" href="javascript:;"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_edit-lemma"></em>编辑</a>
</div>
<table log-set-param="table_view" class="table-view log-set-param"><tr><th width="148">歌名</th><th width="173">作曲</th><th width="158">作词</th><th width="60">演唱</th><th width="51">备注</th></tr><tr><td width="149" align="left" valign="middle">《一又二分之一的夏天》</td><td width="173" align="left" valign="middle">吴智勋</td><td width="158" align="left" valign="middle">红冷</td><td width="60" align="left" valign="middle"><a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%BE%90%E7%92%90/51957" data-lemmaid="51957">徐璐</a></td><td width="51" align="left" valign="middle">片头曲<sup>[6]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[6]_14771740">&nbsp;</a>
</td></tr><tr><td width="149" align="left" valign="middle">《Let it Rain》</td><td width="173" align="left" valign="middle">Ji SangHong&amp;尼坤</td><td width="158" align="left" valign="middle">尼坤</td><td width="60" align="left" valign="middle"><a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%B0%BC%E5%9D%A4">尼坤</a></td><td width="51" align="left" valign="middle">片尾曲</td></tr><tr><td align="left" valign="middle" colspan="1" rowspan="1">《Parisienne WalkWays》</td><td width="35" align="left" valign="middle" colspan="1" rowspan="1">Phil Lynott</td><td width="158" align="left" valign="middle" colspan="1" rowspan="1">Gary Moore</td><td width="60" align="left" valign="middle" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><a target=_blank href="/item/%E4%BA%8E%E6%96%87%E6%96%87">于文文</a></td><td width="51" align="left" valign="middle" colspan="1" rowspan="1">插曲</td></tr><tr><td align="left" valign="middle" colspan="1" rowspan="1">《I&#39;ll Always Be The Same For You》</td><td width="35" align="left" valign="middle" colspan="1" rowspan="1">于文文</td><td width="158" align="left" valign="middle" colspan="1" rowspan="1">王宛之</td><td width="60" align="left" valign="middle" colspan="1" rowspan="1"><a target=_blank href="/item/%E4%BA%8E%E6%96%87%E6%96%87">于文文</a></td><td width="51" align="left" valign="middle" colspan="1" rowspan="1">插曲</td></tr><tr><td align="left" valign="middle" colspan="1" rowspan="1">《爱不爱我》</td><td width="35" align="left" valign="middle" colspan="1" rowspan="1">周晓鸥、朝洛蒙、李小俊、李瑛、王笑冬</td><td width="158" align="left" valign="middle" colspan="1" rowspan="1">周晓鸥、朝洛蒙、李小俊、李瑛、王笑冬</td><td width="60" align="left" valign="middle" colspan="1" rowspan="1">周晓鸥</td><td width="51" align="left" valign="middle" colspan="1" rowspan="1">插曲</td></tr><tr><td align="left" valign="middle" colspan="1" rowspan="1">《你的微笑》</td><td width="35" align="left" valign="middle" colspan="1" rowspan="1">阿沁</td><td width="158" align="left" valign="middle" colspan="1" rowspan="1">阿沁 陈建宁 詹雯婷 谢宥慧 彭资闵</td><td width="60" align="left" valign="middle" colspan="1" rowspan="1">飞儿乐团</td><td width="51" align="left" valign="middle" colspan="1" rowspan="1">插曲</td></tr></table><div class="para" label-module="para"><b></b></div><div class="anchor-list">
<a name="6" class="lemma-anchor para-title" ></a>
<a name="sub14771740_6" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
<a name="幕后花絮" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
</div><div class="para-title level-2" label-module="para-title">
<h2 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">一又二分之一的夏天</span>幕后花絮</h2>
<a class="edit-icon j-edit-link" data-edit-dl="6" href="javascript:;"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_edit-lemma"></em>编辑</a>
</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">1、徐璐爆料蒋劲夫很顽皮，拍摄时不仅频频NG<div class="lemma-picture text-pic layout-right" style="width:220px; float: right;">
<a class="image-link" nslog-type="9317" 
			href="/pic/%E4%B8%80%E5%8F%88%E4%BA%8C%E5%88%86%E4%B9%8B%E4%B8%80%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%8F%E5%A4%A9/6110331/0/242dd42a2834349b09601360cbea15ce37d3bef4?fr=lemma&ct=single" target="_blank"
		title="" style="width:220px;height:146px;">
<img  class="lazy-img" src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAMAAAAoyzS7AAAAGXRFWHRTb2Z0d2FyZQBBZG9iZSBJbWFnZVJlYWR5ccllPAAAAAZQTFRF9fX1AAAA0VQI3QAAAAxJREFUeNpiYAAIMAAAAgABT21Z4QAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==" data-src="https://gss2.bdstatic.com/9fo3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/s%3D220/sign=0853332108d162d981ee651e21dea950/242dd42a2834349b09601360cbea15ce37d3bef4.jpg"  alt="" style="width:220px;height:146px;"/>
</a>
</div>笑场，还会摆臀扭腰、可爱撒娇。<sup>[7]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[7]_14771740">&nbsp;</a>
</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">2、拍摄被尼坤不小心推入水戏时，徐璐当时很紧张，并且还现场演唱了经典神曲《<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%BF%90%E5%BF%91/2586697" data-lemmaid="2586697">忐忑</a>》。<sup>[8]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[8]_14771740">&nbsp;</a>
</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">3、在拍摄过程中，其他几位主演主动承担起中文老师的职责，教尼坤说中文。魏大勋戏称担心不会中文的他会被欺负，所以最开始教尼坤说“你傻”并恶作剧地告诉他，“你傻”的意思是“你很好”。尼坤学会后见到人就热情地说“你傻”，逗得大家发笑。<sup>[9]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[9]_14771740">&nbsp;</a>
</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">4、在拍戏过程中，不明情况的蒋劲夫还和导演商量怎么表演。得到导演同意后，他背对镜头认真演起来，当他转过身，却发现尼坤捧着生日蛋糕站在他面前，和剧组一起过他的22岁生日。<sup>[9]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[9]_14771740">&nbsp;</a>
</div><div class="anchor-list">
<a name="7" class="lemma-anchor para-title" ></a>
<a name="sub14771740_7" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
<a name="幕后制作" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
</div><div class="para-title level-2" label-module="para-title">
<h2 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">一又二分之一的夏天</span>幕后制作</h2>
<a class="edit-icon j-edit-link" data-edit-dl="7" href="javascript:;"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_edit-lemma"></em>编辑</a>
</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><b>创作背景</b></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">该剧想要讲述的是一个关于青春和成长的故事<a class="lemma-album layout-right nslog:10000206" title="尼坤采访图"  href="/pic/%E4%B8%80%E5%8F%88%E4%BA%8C%E5%88%86%E4%B9%8B%E4%B8%80%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%8F%E5%A4%A9/6110331/8924005/9c16fdfaaf51f3de441d133f96eef01f3a29793a?fr=lemma&ct=cover" target="_blank"  style="width:221px;" nslog-type="10000206">
<div class="album-wrap" style="width:219px;height:143px;">
<img class="picture" alt="尼坤采访图" src="https://gss0.bdstatic.com/94o3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/c0%3Dbaike60%2C5%2C5%2C60%2C20/sign=fae99d6379f40ad101e9cfb136457aba/9c16fdfaaf51f3de441d133f96eef01f3a29793a.jpg" style="width:219px;height:143px;"/>
</div>
<div class="description">
尼坤采访图<span class="number">(9张)</span>
</div>
<div class="albumBg">
<div class="albumBgFir" style="width:213px;"></div>
<div class="albumBgSec" style="width:207px;"></div>
</div>
</a>
，在内容上融合了偶像剧和情景剧，既有爱情、友情、浪漫、梦想等元素，又着力于轻松、立体、鲜明的人物特点，致力于创作出有别于以往的校园励志偶像剧。<sup>[10]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[10]_14771740">&nbsp;</a>
</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para"><b>制作过程</b></div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">该剧于2013年7月15日开机，在希腊、北京、厦门等取景<sup>[11]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[11]_14771740">&nbsp;</a>
，剧组采取量身定做的方式，为剧中多位主演倾力打造多款造型，不管是服装还是妆发，均根据角色的性格特点专门设计。在技术上与佳能合作，运用佳能4K超高清影像设备，用高质量画面更好地体现青春独有的靓丽色彩。<sup>[7]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[7]_14771740">&nbsp;</a>
最后于2013年10月杀青。<sup>[12]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[12]_14771740">&nbsp;</a>
</div><div class="anchor-list">
<a name="8" class="lemma-anchor para-title" ></a>
<a name="sub14771740_8" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
<a name="播出信息" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
</div><div class="para-title level-2" label-module="para-title">
<h2 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">一又二分之一的夏天</span>播出信息</h2>
<a class="edit-icon j-edit-link" data-edit-dl="8" href="javascript:;"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_edit-lemma"></em>编辑</a>
</div>
<table log-set-param="table_view" class="table-view log-set-param" data-sort="sortDisabled"><tr><th width="63">播出平台</th><th width="75">播出日期</th><th width="66">播出剧场</th><th width="127">播出时间</th><th width="246">备注</th></tr><tr><td width="63" align="center" valign="center" rowspan="2"><a target=_blank href="/item/%E4%B8%9C%E6%96%B9%E5%8D%AB%E8%A7%86">东方卫视</a></td><td width="75" align="center" valign="center">2014.06.23</td><td width="66" align="center" valign="center">梦想剧场</td><td width="127" align="center" valign="center">19：30——21：30</td><td width="246" align="left" valign="top" rowspan="2">2014年6月23日起<a target=_blank href="/item/%E4%B8%9C%E6%96%B9%E5%8D%AB%E8%A7%86">东方卫视</a>梦想剧场每晚19:30首播第1-6集。后调整6月26日起每天14:00下午剧场续播由第7集开始。<sup>[1]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[1]_14771740">&nbsp;</a>
</td></tr><tr><td width="80" height="39" align="center" valign="center">2014.06.26</td><td width="42" height="39" align="center" valign="center">下午剧场</td><td width="93" height="39" align="center" valign="center"><div class="para" label-module="para">14：00——17：00</div>
</td></tr></table><div class="anchor-list">
<a name="9" class="lemma-anchor para-title" ></a>
<a name="sub14771740_9" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
<a name="影片评价" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
</div><div class="para-title level-2" label-module="para-title">
<h2 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">一又二分之一的夏天</span>影片评价</h2>
<a class="edit-icon j-edit-link" data-edit-dl="9" href="javascript:;"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_edit-lemma"></em>编辑</a>
</div>
<div class="anchor-list">
<a name="9_1" class="lemma-anchor para-title" ></a>
<a name="sub14771740_9_1" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
<a name="正面评价" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
<a name="9-1" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
</div><div class="para-title level-3" label-module="para-title">
<h3 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">一又二分之一的夏天</span>正面评价</h3>
</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">该剧镜头画面唯美，风格清新<i>（京华时报评）</i>。<sup>[13]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[13]_14771740">&nbsp;</a>
</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">偶像剧的制作团队，新鲜实力派的演员阵容，不仅能够带给人们青春的回忆，还能引发对校园生活的眷恋，这不仅是一部能与90后、00后产生共鸣的青春校园剧，同时它也属于为青春、为理想努力拼搏奋斗过的80后<i>（腾讯娱乐评）</i><sup>[14]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[14]_14771740">&nbsp;</a>
。轻松愉快的剧情也给现在颇有压力的生活吹来一股清新的风<i>（新浪娱乐评）</i>。<sup>[15]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[15]_14771740">&nbsp;</a>
</div><div class="anchor-list">
<a name="9_2" class="lemma-anchor para-title" ></a>
<a name="sub14771740_9_2" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
<a name="负面评价" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
<a name="9-2" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
</div><div class="para-title level-3" label-module="para-title">
<h3 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">一又二分之一的夏天</span>负面评价</h3>
</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">演员的表演在观众眼里有着不同的评价，例如徐璐饰演的罗曼，部分观众觉得可爱不做作、自然<i>（北青网评）</i>。<sup>[16]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[16]_14771740">&nbsp;</a>
但也有一部分观众觉得演得太过，演技浮夸，如动不动就大喊大叫。剧情部分，有些观众觉得剧情老套，如马俊才、文婷婷、李修齐和罗曼的四角恋<i>（中国江西网-大江时评）</i><sup>[17]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[17]_14771740">&nbsp;</a>
。</div>
<div class="anchor-list">
<a name="a" class="lemma-anchor a" ></a>
